<ul id="mwBEM"><li id="mwBEQ">For God in the Quran (Allah), see <i id="mwBEU">Allah</i> by Zeki Saritoprak, pp. 33–40.</li>
<li id="mwBEY">For eschatology, see <i id="mwBEc">Eschatology</i> by Zeki Saritoprak, pp. 194–199.</li>
<li id="mwBEg">For searching the Arabic text on the internet and writing, see <i id="mwBEk">Cyberspace and the Qur'an</i> by Andrew Rippin, pp. 159–163.</li>
<li id="mwBEo">For calligraphy, see by <i id="mwBEs">Calligraphy and the Qur'an</i> by Oliver Leaman, pp. 130–135.</li>
<li id="mwBEw">For translation, see <i id="mwBE0">Translation and the Qur'an</i> by Afnan Fatani, pp. 657–669.</li>
